  "summary": "clean-my-pc exfiltrates host information to attacker-controlled endpoint",
  "details": "The package's collect.js gathers host-identifying data via os.hostname() and os.homedir(), enumerates filesystem paths with fs.existsSync, imports child_process, and POSTs the collected data to the hardcoded endpoint http://aab.sportsontheweb.net. The package name suggests a benign 'PC cleanup' utility, but the shipped code is a system-information stealer that beacons to an attacker-controlled host on execution. There is no legitimate reason for a cleanup utility to transmit host identity and filesystem reconnaissance to an external third-party domain.",
